### Central point of puppet:
/etc/puppetlabs/code/environments/production/manifests
########################################### EXAPLE 1 ##############################################
nano site.pp:
node default{
  notify { 'Hello, World!!!!!' : }
  file { 'helloworld' :
    ensure => present,
    path => '/tmp/helloworld',
    content => 'Hello World!',
    mode => '0644',
    owner => 'root',
    group => 'root'
  }
}

### Here
default - to all nodes
notify - Show message on the screen

### Result on the node1:
